children.text: Start the year with the right foot by getting hold of your finances.
With this template you can input your expenses and income to get a detailed summary of cashflows by type as well charts that show how much you are spending on each category so far and by month.

This is your financial summary based on the information you input below under 'My Data'. 

Your can Interact with the below data view to explore your financial by different time periods and categories: 

Time Period: Click
On the Money Spent in 2023 chart, you can see how much you are spending in each category along the year
On the Money Spend each Month chart, you can see how your expenses progress along the year
On this section, you can input your cashflows for each month. There is a table for each month to make your expenses easy to categorize and aggregate. Expand the 'show table' to fill out every month.
This section has the calculations that power this template. You don't need to update these.
